[Since July 2016, Namibia has reported 5 outbreaks of LSD. The outbreaks were located in Omaheke region. The event is still continuing. See event summary and updated map at, http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review/viewsummary?reportid=20410.

Maps of Namibia can be seen at http://www.mapsofworld.com/namibia/maps/namibia-political-map.jpg and https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=4517495,20492. Omaheke is a region adjacent to Otjozondjupa region in Namibia. - Mod.CRD]
